import React from 'react' const CardPopout = ({ heroInfo }) => { return (
{heroInfo.base_hp}
+{heroInfo.hp_regen}
{heroInfo.base_mana}
+{heroInfo.mana_regen}
{heroInfo.min_dmg}{'-'}{heroInfo.max_dmg}
{heroInfo.BAT}
{heroInfo.atck_range}
{heroInfo.projectile_spd}
{heroInfo.armor}
{heroInfo.move_spd}
{heroInfo.turn_rate}
{heroInfo.day_vision + '/' +heroInfo.night_vision}
{heroInfo.str_strt}
+{heroInfo.str_gain}
{heroInfo.agi_strt}
+{heroInfo.agi_gain}
{heroInfo.int_strt}
+{heroInfo.int_gain}
) } export default CardPopout
